description:
You won't wanna miss this diverse panel of startup leaders provide tips and tools to get your startup off the ground and win over investors. Learn some of the biggest mistakes entrepreneurs make when pitching to angels and how to avoid those pitfalls.

Panel includes:  Nikki Johnson- Huston, Esq., Nisa Amoils, Yasmine Mustafa, and moderated by Ellen Weber-Moderator.
title: How to get your startup off the ground and attract investors
